10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Rephrase.ai is best suited for personalized marketing videos, sales outreach at scale, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Sora, meanwhile, shines for high quality realistic video generation, creative professionals, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2019, Rephrase.ai describes itself as \"Create personalized AI videos at scale.\" Sora, established in 2024, positions itself as \"OpenAI's text-to-video model for realistic video generation.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Sora** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0). However, this does not mean Rephrase.ai is a poor choice — far from it. Rephrase.ai excels in its own right, particularly for personalized marketing videos and sales outreach at scale.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value stunning video quality, go with Sora. If excellent personalization api matters more to you, Rephrase.ai is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
